name: I’m always nervous before Miami-FSU games. Always. My ‘Canes are favored by two TDS, are at home in one of the loudest stadiums in the country, and on paper this shouldn’t be close. Go ‘Canes! Beat FSU like a drum!🤞🏻 🙌🏻 🏈
